<!--EZCODE QUOTE START--><blockquote><strong><em>Quote:</em></strong><hr>There are so many words other than those that you could use. I don't care if you're using them to insult someone or using them to boost your fragile ego.<hr></blockquote><!--EZCODE QUOTE END--><br>
